These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-7-1::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: soul, hip-hop, gospel, country, salsa, disco, folk
1. the fan of folk is in the middle##1
2. the fan of soul is on the left or right of the fan of folk##3
3. the fan of gospel is somewhere between the fan of disco and the fan of folk##7
4. the fan of hip-hop is somewhere to the right of the fan of soul##5
5. the fan of salsa is on the left of the fan of disco##1
6. the fan of soul is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |   2    |    3    |   4    |    5    |     6     |  7   |
| Music-Genre   | salsa | disco | gospel | folk | soul | hip-hop | country |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-7-2::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: satire, romance, comedy, family, documentary, crime, spy
 1. the person watching comedy movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching family movies##5
 2. the person watching comedy movies is somewhere between the person watching spy movies and the person watching romance movies##7
 3. the person watching romance movies is on the left or right of the person watching documentary movies##3
 4. the person watching satire movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching family movies##5
 5. the person watching family movies is somewhere between the person watching satire movies and the person watching documentary movies##7
 6. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
 7. the person watching crime movies is on the left or right of the person watching family movies##3
 8. the person watching crime movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching family movies##5
 9. the person watching documentary movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching romance movies##5
10. the person watching romance movies is on the left or right of the person watching documentary movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2       |    3     |    4    |      5      |     6      |   7    |
| Movie-Genre   | spy | comedy | documentary | romance | crime | family | satire |

