.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-7-3::.
The people use 7 different means of transport: quad-bike, ship, motorbike, tram, bus, taxi, airplane
1. the person driving the ship is somewhere between the person driving the quad-bike and the person driving the bus##7
2. the person driving the bus is somewhere between the person driving the motorbike and the person driving the ship##7
3. the person driving the taxi is somewhere to the left of the person driving the bus##5
4. the person driving the taxi is somewhere between the person driving the airplane and the person driving the quad-bike##7
5. the person driving the ship is somewhere to the right of the person driving the bus##5
6. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere between the person driving the ship and the person driving the taxi##7
7. the person driving the taxi is somewhere to the left of the person driving the bus##5
8. the person driving the tram is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1  |   2   |   3    |   4   |     5      |  6  |     7      |
| Transport   | airplane | taxi | motorbike | bus | ship | quad-bike | tram |

