6. the person driving the trike is somewhere to the left of the person driving the motorbike##5
7. the person driving the subway is somewhere between the person driving the bus and the person driving the trike##7
8. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
9. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere to the right of the person driving the tram##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |  2   |   3   |  4   |  5   |     6     |    7    |
| Transport   | tram | trike | motorbike | subway | bus | skateboard | jet-ski |

