.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-7-6::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: skydiving, fishing, hiking, dancing, filmmaking, rock-climbing, singing
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
2. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##5
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3
5. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##3
6. the person who's hobby is hiking is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
7. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
8. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the far left or far right##3
9. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere between the person who's hobby is hiking and the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |      3      |      4       |     5     |    6    |   7   |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing | singing | skydiving | filmmaking | dancing | hiking | fishing |

