 2. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere to the right of the owner of the chinchilla##5
 3. the owner of the fish is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hedgehog##5
 4. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left or right of the owner of the mouse##3
 5. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere between the owner of the goldfish and the owner of the rat##7
 6. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 7. the owner of the horse is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the owner of the rat is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
10. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere to the right of the owner of the mouse##5

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1      |  2  |  3   |   4    |   5   |  6   |  7   |
| Pet   | horse | chinchilla | goldfish | fish | mouse | hedgehog | rat |

